FBIS4-9676 "drlat062_g_94003" FBIS-LAT-94-062 Daily Report 30 Mar 1994 Guatemala U.S. Tourist Shot, Robbed U.S. Tourist Shot, Robbed PA3003220494 Guatemala City Cadena de Emisoras Unidas in Spanish 2115 GMT 30 Mar 94 PA3003220494 Guatemala City Cadena de Emisoras Unidas Spanish BFN [Report by Jorge Cendis from the "News Patrol" newscast] [Text] A U.S. tourist identified as (Duncan Milliet Aitena), 42, has been attacked by the occupants of a vehicle that sped away after stripping him of his valuables. This occurred while the tourist was riding a motorcycle, license plate No. M-91,869. The victim was shot four times in the body and was dying as he was taken to the emergency room of the [name indistinct] Medical Center by paramedics of the Municipal Firefighters Corps who came to help the victim aboard Unit No. R-39.
